  "line_count": 69,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02857:e06677d16ac0]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02858:f6d20f28e6fe]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02859:714913c5ab2b]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02860:f4379f536ddd]]\n\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02861:eb8a21527b65]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02862:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n设气体总质量[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02863:297422400257]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P02864:2906c2febeb4]]\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02865:0b75cf5f9a9e]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02866:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02867:04983af0ce41]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02868:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n水蒸气分子取 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02869:d11cd7716d1c]]，氢气和氧气取 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02870:bc9aeda22a69]]。设初态有 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02871:2e1139cd855c]] mol 水蒸气， [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02872:2e1139cd855c]] mol 水蒸气分解后生成 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02873:2e1139cd855c]] mol [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02874:97523f600427]] 和 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02875:6685082d56d5]] mol [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02876:55df487af380]]。由 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02877:6275d64f8f65]]，\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02878:02404c0f4060]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02879:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02880:308be532af8d]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02881:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n平动能转化为内能增加。因此设气体质量为[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02882:297422400257]]，由能量守恒写出\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02883:b86c9005682a]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02884:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02885:860c00acc9b9]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02886:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02887:1187a254f61a]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02888:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02889:78c1359e99e4]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02890:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02891:7fd648fd7cba]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02892:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
